steps.name: Open Loek and perform smoke testing using mentioned scenarios...
user goes to dashboard and performs smoke test > Click On Company Profile, Company Public Profile, My Profile, My Public Profile

go to building app and perform smoke test > Click On Building, Building Unit, Building Room, Building Element, Building Surface, Building tenant, Building document, Building key, Building invoice, Building disturbance, Building contact

go to building unit and perform smoke test > Click On BuildingUnit, Building unit element, Building unit tenant, Building unit document, Building unit key address, Building unit invoice address, Building unit disturbance, Building unit contact
go to building complex and perform smoke test > Click On BuildingComplex, Building complex key address, Building complex invoice address, Building complex disturbance, Building complex contact
